{
  "chapter": 36,
  "chapter_summary": "王万武死于阴柔掌力，铁震天断定他因奸细身份被无十三灭口。绝大师失踪，大婉下落不明，马如龙坚持留下寻找，谢玉宝因担心他赴死而激动劝阻，马如龙坦言若失踪的是她也会如此，铁震天由此悟出有情人更不怕死并决定同行。众人听见马嘶追出，发现车夫倒毙、车马被劫，遂以八步赶蝉、天马行空等轻功追赶。谢玉宝判断人力终会落后，俞六赶来载众人继续追，指出直路通向死谷。众人以不计后果的决心追去，却不知道死谷真相并非他们想象。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "他怎么会死？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "他当然要死，做奸细的人，本来就是这种下场。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "你认为是无十三杀他灭口的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们走吧。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 37,
      "line_end": 37
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "走？到哪里去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 39,
      "line_end": 39
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "随便到哪里去，只要赶快离开这里。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 41,
      "line_end": 41
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我们走，你呢？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 43,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "我……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 45,
      "line_end": 45
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我知道你要干什么，你要留在这里找大婉，找不到她，你是绝不肯走的。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 47,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "难道我不该找她？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 51,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你当然应该找她，但是你为什么不想想？你是不是能找得到她？找到了又怎么样？难道你能从无十三手里救她出来？难道你以为无十三不敢杀你？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 53,
      "line_end": 57
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你一心一意只想找她，除了她之外，别的人难道都不是人？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 59,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你为什么不替别人想想，为什么不替你自己想想？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 61,
      "line_end": 61
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "好，你要找死就自己一个人去死，我们走。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 69,
      "line_end": 71
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "其实你也该明白的，如果失踪了的不是大婉是你，我也一样会留下来找你。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 75,
      "line_end": 77
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也明白了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 81,
      "line_end": 81
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "你明白了什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 83,
      "line_end": 83
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "本来我总以为，不怕死的都是无情人，现在我才知道错了，原来有情人更不怕死，因为他们心里已经有了情，已经把别的事全都忘得干干净净。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 85,
      "line_end": 87
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你不走，我们也不走，不找到大婉，谁都不会走。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 89,
      "line_end": 91
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "追！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 105,
      "line_end": 105
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们绝对追不上的。拉车的四匹马都是好马，不但经过训练，而且很有耐力，我坐在车上的时候，已经算过它们跑得有多快。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 131,
      "line_end": 133
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "开始的时候，我们比他们快，所以现在我们好像还能追得上，但是再过三五里之后，我们就会渐渐慢下来，它们却反而会越跑越快。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 133,
      "line_end": 135
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_liu",
      "speaker_name": "俞六",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们一定可以追上去的，这是条直路，他们只有这条路可走。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 147,
      "line_end": 149
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "众人",
      "listener": "char_yu_liu",
      "text": "这条路是到什么地方去的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 151,
      "line_end": 151
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_liu",
      "speaker_name": "俞六",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "死谷。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 153,
      "line_end": 153
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不管怎么样，死谷总不是人人都能去的地方，我们能去看看也算不容易。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 163,
      "line_end": 165
    }
  ],
